  <brief_title>Study the Effects of CYP2C Polymorphisms on the Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of Glipizide</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study the Effects of CYP2C9 and CYP2C19 Polymorphisms on the Pharmacokinetics and Pharmacodynamics of Glipizide in Healthy Chinese Subject</official_title>
